 that I intend on leveling up.. a ranger though... you guys are best on info so I figured I asked you.<br>
<br>
Options: 31/35 2hb, 32/36 2hs, 35/35 2hs *forgot name and not sure if it's level restricted*, 9/18 4 dex 4wis 1hp, 11/20 6dex 6agi 45hp 1hb, 12/20 2hb, 12/22 1hs frostbringer, 9/19 defiance 1hs, 9/19 lamentation, 10/18 crafted warsword. <p>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=432618  <br>
 <br>
 <br>
 <br>
 Bandory [61 High Priest] <br>
<br>
&quot;How long do you have to pull your reserve in the event of a main canopy malfunction? The rest of your life ! <br>
